Alisson: &quot;From last year to here, our team has evolved a lot. I can control when I have to control and we have worked more on ball possession.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Alisson: &ldquo;Because it was very vertical [last season], we would take counter-attacks. This year we were more consistent, more knowledgeable in-game.&rdquo;

Guardiola: &ldquo;I cannot find a better one than Liverpool. In that level, that high level, it's not just down to mental factors or skill, power or technique, it's a mix for everything.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Guardiola: &ldquo;I have the feeling that they made us a better team. Always the value of the titles you win depends on the quality of the contender, your big rival.&rdquo;

Alberto Moreno has admitted that he would like to return to Sevilla this summer.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;Sevilla is my home, I would like to return.&rdquo;

